{"tid":168503,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"每個男人最少都有三種人格","createTime":"2017-03-23T14:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T15:04:03.000Z","uid":57364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07d928e3f096b5c514f0b9f11440360293698e62","tid":168503,"uid":57364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"聖人模式同狗公模式同普通模式<br />\n<br />\n聖人模式一啟動成個世界會即刻唔同哂，諗野勁清晰，仲會思考下人生，好哲學家。<br />\n<br />\n普通模式就係介乎於聖人同狗公之間，(表面) 係一個紳士。<br />\n<br />\n狗公模式就係精蟲上腦，發情，甚至會造出匪夷所思嘅行為。"},{"pid":"bfc2aebd53e0da3d023c011d150d459f9dbb4cca","tid":168503,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c965d751cd5c5c62b840223e34d57185a9e8feba","tid":168503,"uid":57364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬而家啟動緊on9模式</blockquote><br />\n我啱啱入左聖人模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5803151ad99fe273fb86bb0fbda95d2e9e5bce4c","tid":168503,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:55:43.000Z","msg":"存聖人，去狗公"},{"pid":"b2cfdc09cd8dcd31f28597be5f1364f5d9609668","tid":168503,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬而家啟動緊on9模式</blockquote><br />\n我啱啱入左聖人模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聖人mode都咁on9你真係叻極有個普<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}